<br>
As for being evil, fuggeddaboudit!  It isn't much of a crutch.<br>
<br>
If you choose an Iksar, you really never need to leave Kunark.  Heck, you can stay in one zone (Field of Bone) up to level 20!  And by then, you'll be tough enough to do some travelling.<br>
<br>
If you choose Troll, there's all sorts of good zones around.  To the north the Deserts of Ro and Oasis will take you to 20 easy, and then head west to Lake Rathe and Karana's.<br>
<br>
You need to go with what you'll be happy with.  I chose Iksar, and I can't even wear the best warrior armor out there!  But heck, I'm having a great time with him.  And that's what its all about.<br>
<br>
Sarassis Kikarsis<br>
23rd Iksar Warrior<br>
